Title: The QCD Trace Anomaly as a Vacuum Effect (The vacuum is a medium is the
  message!)
Authors: J. Grundberg and T. H. Hansson (Stockhom University)
Comments: 18 pages, USITP 94-11
Journal-ref: Annals Phys. 242 (1995) 413-428
\\
  We use arguments taken from the electrodynamics of media to deduce the QCD
trace anomaly from the expression for the vacuum energy in the presence of an
external color magnetic field.
